hâu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%C3%A1i-tr%C3%AC-3/poem-Se3JVs_zS4GXJWFmZ5v2og">Tái trì 3 - 載馳 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%C4%83n-s%C6%B0-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-lrInu8EHZW2WFXctHWZmxA">Tống Trăn sư kỳ 1 - 送臻師其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/V%C3%A3n-t%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-c%C3%B4ng/poem-cDElVqf2JwRbA8T7Kf-a_A">Vãn tư đồ công - 輓司徒公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
